history.content:
16B Expansion Spring 2020

16B has expanded to hold a max enrollment of 1,044. At this time, only students who qualify for the reserved seating can enroll in the class. If you do not qualify for the reserved seating you will need to wait until the reserved seats expire, 1/6/2020. The new reserved seats are based on the number of students on the waitlist under each category.

If you are on the waitlist for a lab that is full and you qualify for the reserved seats, I recommend you drop the class and re-add it with a new lab that still has open seats. This means that you will be placed at the bottom of the waitlist but you should be enrolled so long as you qualify for the reserved seats.

If you have questions or need assistance, please email ee-scheduling@eecs.berkeley.edu and be sure to include your SID.
